title: Republican Gov. John Kasich says he's a 'troublemaker'
text: The Ohio governor, who is struggling to say in the nomination race, has described himself on Monday at the University of Richmond as a "troublemaker" who's been at the center of battles to balance the government budgets for decades. Kasich is one of several presidential hopefuls visiting Virginia, a competitive state expected to help decide the 2016 presidential contest. ...
